We apply for all the three badges, i.e., available, functional, and reusable. The reasons are as follows.

Available: The artifacts relevant to the paper have been placed on [https://www.zenodo.org](https://www.zenodo.org/) and can be downloaded open sourced.

Functional: The artifacts are documented, consistent, complete, exercisable, and include appropriate evidence of verification and validation.

Reusable: The artifacts are well organized and carefully documented. It is facilitating to reuse them.